00:23:02,170 --> 00:23:03,490
Let me teach you how to read,

369
00:23:03,490 --> 00:23:04,190
so that in the future

370
00:23:04,190 --> 00:23:06,920
you can understand maps
and official documents.

371
00:23:12,630 --> 00:23:13,110
Come.

