[Tomb of My Old Friend Qiao]

398
00:26:03,910 --> 00:26:04,870
Jin'an

399
00:26:05,470 --> 00:26:07,130
is a wolf in sheep's clothing.

400
00:26:08,220 --> 00:26:09,950
But he treats the General well,

401
00:26:10,030 --> 00:26:11,030
so he's a good guy.

